I"*<h1 id="openproject-746">OpenProject 7.4.6</h1>

<p>We released OpenProject 7.4.6. The release contains several bug fixes.
We recommend the update to the current version.</p>

<h4 id="support-for-ubuntu-1804">Support for Ubuntu 18.04.</h4>

<p>OpenProject 7.4.6 packaged installation introduces support for Ubuntu
18.04. 
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/27799">#27799</a>)</p>

<h4 id="bug-fixes-and-changes">Bug fixes and changes</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Fixed: Poor performance when adding several work packages to a large
tree
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/27878">#27878</a>)</li>
  <li>Fixed: Saving filter-selected list Custom Field with single value
results in error
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/27833">#27833</a>)</li>
  <li>Fixed: Progress calculation for parents in bulk edit was not applied
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/27975">#27975</a>)</li>
  <li>Fixed: CSS columns display in Chrome versions 65 to 66 due to
backface-visibility
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/27823">#27823</a>)</li>
  <li>Improved: Performance on global activities page
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/27582">#27582</a>)</li>
</ul>

<p>Special thanks go to all OpenProject contributors for <a href="https://www.openproject.org/development/report-a-bug/">reporting
bugs</a> and helping
us to reproduce them.</p>

